\newlabel{tab:size-d50}{{3}{8}{Median $d_{50}$ by cluster-size bin, separately for content-coherent and noise clusters, on two models. At each size bin, coherent and noise clusters have nearly identical median $d_{50}$. The scaling with $n$ is monotonic for both coherent and noise clusters}{table.3}{}}
