\newlabel{fig:size-bins}{{2}{8}{Median $d_{50}$ by cluster-size bin on Gemma-3 4B (left) and OLMo-2 7B final checkpoint (right), split by content coherence. Within each bin, coherent and noise clusters have nearly identical $d_{50}$; the Hernandez 5--22D band (shaded) corresponds roughly to clusters of size $n \lesssim 75$--$90$ on both models}{figure.2}{}}
