\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces OLMo-2 trajectory across seven checkpoints. Euclidean pass rate (red) shows a cliff at 214B tokens that spherical pass rate (blue) does not, indicating the cliff is a clustering-method artifact. Content coherence (green, right axis) shows a sharp emergence between 214B and 911B tokens that neither pass-rate curve tracks --- this is the informative training-dynamics signal.}}{12}{figure.5}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:trajectory}{{5}{12}{OLMo-2 trajectory across seven checkpoints. Euclidean pass rate (red) shows a cliff at 214B tokens that spherical pass rate (blue) does not, indicating the cliff is a clustering-method artifact. Content coherence (green, right axis) shows a sharp emergence between 214B and 911B tokens that neither pass-rate curve tracks --- this is the informative training-dynamics signal}{figure.5}{}}
